data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Pueblo West! This stunning property offers the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and spacious living. Boasting five bedrooms, three baths, and a three-car garage, this residence is an example of modern living. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warm embrace of beautiful hardwood floors that adorn the main level, creating an inviting and elegant atmosphere. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living spaces, providing a perfect setting for gatherings and entertaining guests. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the expansive kitchen, complete with a center island that serves as the focal point. The kitchen is a hub for socializing, ensuring that no one is ever far from the action. The main level is home to a spacious primary bedroom, offering a tranquil retreat with its five-piece bath. Imagine unwinding in luxury after a long day, soaking in the tub or enjoying the serenity of your private oasis. The lower level of this residence is a walk-out basement, adding another dimension to the living space. Whether it's a game room, home theater, or a versatile space for guests, the possibilities are endless. Situated on a sprawling over one-acre lot, the outdoor space is just as impressive as the interior. Enjoy the beauty of nature and the vastness of your own piece of Colorado from the comfort of your backyard. The three-car garage ensures ample space for vehicles and additional storage. Be sure to see this great property!
